Titolo: The Legend of Heroes: A Tear of Vermillion

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: The Legend of Heroes: A Tear of Vermillion, known in Japan as The Legend of Heroes IV: Akai Shizuku, is a role-playing video game developed by Nihon Falcom. It is the fourth game in The Legend of Heroes series, and the second in the "Gagharv Trilogy". Originally released for the NEC PC-9801 in 1996, it was later released for the PlayStation in 1998 and Microsoft Windows in 2000. A remake was released for the PlayStation Portable in 2005, which was the first North American release of a Legend of Heroes game since Dragon Slayer: The Legend of Heroes for the TurboGrafx-16. The North American release dropped the number from the title, and was known as simply The Legend of Heroes: A Tear of Vermillion.

Genere: Role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
